<table  border=0 cellpadding=2 cellspacing=0 awidth=100%><a name=10229125435463></a><form action=http://eqdb.allakhazam.com/strategy/mrate.pl name=f10229125435463><tr><td id=headerrow><a id=sj href=classes.html?class=2&mid=10229125435463>RE: Why to be a rogue</a> <a id=fs8 href=classes.html?class=2&mid=10229125435463#post><img src=http://everquest.allakhazam.com/static/reply.gif border=0 alt="Reply..." height=16 width=16></a></td><td align=right id=headerrow valign=bottom><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=73658><span id=Sage>DavivMcD</span></a>, <span id=Sage>Sage</span><br><span id=notbold>292 posts</td></tr>
	   <tr><td colspan=1 id=headerrow>Posted @ Sat, Jun 1st 2:32 AM 2002</td>
