 night to 24 and am still going strong as both a solo and a tank. To help with perspective, examples of my equipment are: Sarnak Emblazoned Tabard (sp?), Banded Leggings, Jagged Chokidai Spine, Crystalline Short Sword (or forged warhammer at times), Rough Ashwood Bow, Faydark Ringmail Sleeves (I'm going for a full set). AGI and DEX are around 125 each and STR at 99. The only problem I have with soloing is one that anyone can have … I can’t watch my own back! :)<br><br>Discussion is good!<br><br>Restyn<br>Rogue of Saryrn Server<br>24 Seasons ... and counting<br><br><br><em id=fs8>Edited, Thu May 30 11:29:58 2002</em><br>&nbsp;<br>Restyn<br>Rogue of Saryrn Server<br>32 Seasons</td></tr>
